    "overview": "奥斯陆发生了一连串带有仪式色彩的凶杀案。一位名探必须理清错综复杂的线索，揭露腐败并克服心魔，才能将凶手绳之以法。",
    "reviews": [],
    "backdrop_url": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/duguBoss/daily-movie-hub@main/data/images/tv_249597_b.jpg",
    "poster_url": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/duguBoss/daily-movie-hub@main/data/images/tv_249597_p.jpg",
    "update_date": "2026-04-26",
